Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a slowpoke, Rita.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, everyone, stay where you are and listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We have some new workers\Njoining us here at the laundry mill today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, ladies, if you'd introduce yourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Bea...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Becky!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.25,0:00:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dorothea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.46,0:00:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Chieko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Priscilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit staring at me, would ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:00:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:01:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone disrespects me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And I knock 'em to Kingdom Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of a cover is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.42,0:01:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a former delinquent who decided to\Nturn over a new leaf when her mother fell ill,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So I went to work, but I can't hide my bad attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an elaborate backstory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the optimal cover for this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.38,0:01:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. The mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison Gas Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,An elusive phantom killer who's been making\Na name for himself in the tabloids.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been assassinating important people\Nwho've shown support for the Commonwealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But we haven't identified any backers.\NWe believe he's working alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we have but to exterminate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I will handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A man who uses poison gas will be an easy opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to find him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what he's trying to accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nerve gas, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought production of nerve gas\Nwas banned by the Geneva Convention.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So where did he get his illegal poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting the ingredients would be difficult, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.21,0:03:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means he's in the Army?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Control had the same idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Gas produced before the Convention\Nis lying unused in military storehouses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean inside the London Wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The storehouses were built\Nbefore the second round of construction,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'd have to go through\Nthe military barracks to get to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The odds are good that our poisoner\Nlives in those barracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How many are housed there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,About 1200.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That many?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How will we find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Disguise ourselves as soldiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the Army is a boys' club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Women would draw too much attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And living in the barracks alongside them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be difficult to maintain a manly facade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Men don't do laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,None of the boys in class-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nerve gas would adhere to his clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And the barracks send all of the men's uniforms\Nto a laundry mill for washing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So we infiltrate the laundry mill\Nand find the uniform that reacts to a pyridine test.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Miss Alice, you can't just\Nmove the desk around without-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like being ordered around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:04:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:04:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what she meant by "optimal cover."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It does keep people from asking questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Your Highness, why did you come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a part of the team, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to you talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You just wanted to see what it was like, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This may be a foolish question, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the master laundress of this establishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That would have to be Marilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Many pardons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that you have the greatest skill with the iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I request your guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,First, watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.83,0:05:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then if you have any questions, just ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese people are odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I can't expect to find it that soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone turn it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's all for this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it's time for a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But we haven't been working an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray! Break time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have some lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.79,0:06:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In two days, we've tested\Na total of 150 articles of clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But we couldn't confirm a single reaction\Nto our chemical test.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, it's gonna take us a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Those women are all too lazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If they would work harder, they could earn more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very strict, aren't you, Miss Chise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it's about time for a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So much work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Put down the iron, Japan Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you. I am not tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You may all rest without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a break! That's the rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You have but one life to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you not give everything your best effort?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I'm trying-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rita!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,These scars...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I told you to take a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The machinery here is junk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't give it a rest every so often, people get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We get paid by the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If we get hurt, we can't earn any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We may not like it, but we do what we can to get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the foreman in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Pwah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You rabble. I don't care who,\Nbut one of you get the foreman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him Franky is here. He'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you are aware, Foreman,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that your payment is due.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So what will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't pay, then I'll run\Nyour sorry little mill into the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I need a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he going to close the mill?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:08:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we bankrupt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I always said that foreman was useless as a manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's going to put a damper on our plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we even going to be paid this month?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know this place was in debt.\NAre we even going to be paid this month?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother's surgery is at the end of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chise, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't pay now, when can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the middle of an important discussion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. And I've come with an important proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to buy this laundry mill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I will pay off the debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That should resolve all the problems, shouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of this, little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not playing a game here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you would really buy the mill, debt and all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop making up stories! A woman, buying the mill!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare raise your hand against a lady,\Nyou piece of garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be such a pigheaded jackass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She says she's gonna buy the mill,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,so shut up and sell it to her, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, what are you even doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking,\Nbuying a mill that's losing money?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If the laundry mill were to close,\Nthat would be the end of our mission, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We just need two more weeks\Nto check all of the soldiers' uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And we need to keep the mill\Nin business until then, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.75,0:10:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have that much money\Nat your disposal, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't intend to let the laundry mill\Nbe a poor investment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You intend to make a profit from it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! Not from that place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't like you, Miss Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we could do anything\Nwith hard work and practice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Ange? Do you think it's impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is impossible for a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you lie to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The machines here have always made\Nsuch terrible noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.46,0:11:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think they've ever seen proper maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd believe that from that stingy foreman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I think if we just fix them up right,\Nthey'll be able to work that much harder for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And the accidents will cease?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is replace the old parts,\Nand it will be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.21,0:11:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We should rearrange them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The workpath is too convoluted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If we line the machines up according to work sequence,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,we can save ourselves a lot of running around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine they placed them\Nin order of when they were purchased.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They do look heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can change that weight to zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I order you as foreman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rearrange the machinery to create\Nthe optimal work path.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, and we'll get all the tools\Norganized while we're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of the girls can't read,\Nso let's have pictures on the signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's repair these pipes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess, may we try the method used in my country?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds fascinating! Tell me about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.21,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.92,0:12:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so organized.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The belts have stopped squeaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a new machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We serviced them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Some dust got mixed in with the old grease,\Nand clogged it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We cleaned it, so it won't stop anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, YOU girls did all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In one night?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, in one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we'll have a fresh start, and work our hardest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have a word?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We know an excellent way to do laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Chieko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When we're sad, we'll all laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to go see our mothers and fathers
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that song?\NWe want to go see our mothers and fathers
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming from the laundry mill.\NWe want to go see our mothers and fathers
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming from the laundry mill.\NWhen we want to cry, we'll all laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When we want to cry, we'll all laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an odd song.\NWhen we want to cry, we'll all laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When we want to cry, we'll all laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can cry tears of joy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,For the whole week.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:13:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We finished so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies of the laundry mill!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we've improved our efficiency,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose you'd like to improve\Nour revenue, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You mean earn more money?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If we wash more, we earn more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's nothing left to wash,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Army won't bring more 'round til the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll just have to get some from other sources.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of you girls could really shine with a little polish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Keep lollygagging\Nand it'll be dark before we're through!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here with a business proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We would like to wash all of your work clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"We"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We look forward to working with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,With you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We already have a launderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:14:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can change that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's let them wash our clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you just complaining about their sloppy work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose we could see how you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.79,0:15:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an awful lot of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a lot of success,\Nthanks to our excellent saleslady.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Rita?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all so pretty, I hardly recognize you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Dorothea taught us how to wear makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What! Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No fair!\NDo me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, save the chatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.71,0:15:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get these clothes in the machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for doing sales, Rita.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this report?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the income and expense report\Nfor the laundry mill Princess purchased.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They've increased revenue 231% since last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho ho, how interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought their job was to find Poison Gas Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasting their time on these frivolities!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What does D say about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That it was a necessary measure\Nin continuing the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I left it on my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that all? They came around collecting laundry,\Nso I gave it to them for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, this guy always does his own laundry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't want your help, Mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Have to do it the way Mummy taught you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn one more round
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best to earn a living
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,To eat delicious food
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When we're tired, we'll all sing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can stop our sighing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use this if you wish.\NSo we can stop our sighing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can stop our sighing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, thanks.\NWhen we're sad, we'll all laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.42,0:17:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When we're sad, we'll all laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A bandage?\NWhen we're sad, we'll all laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You wear it like this.\NWhen we're sad, we'll all laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You wear it like this.\NWe want to go see our mothers and fathers
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to go see our mothers and fathers
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called a hachimaki.\NWe want to go see our mothers and fathers
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When we want to cry, we'll all laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In my country, we use them to rouse our fighting spirit.\NWhen we want to cry, we'll all laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.\NWhen we want to cry, we'll all laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When we want to cry, we'll all laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can cry tears of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Dorothy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a way of attracting things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Private William Ricard, Platoon 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,His unit's barracks is right above the storehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he's the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll go get the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Put the evidence in this bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:18:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,None who work here feel the need\Nto walk with such cat-like tread.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Scoundrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Chieko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Marilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Long live the Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Chieko and the others\Nhaven't come to work in days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think they have tummyaches, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies, would you all come here, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Why are we having a meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are our wages going up again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided to step down as foreman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.71,0:20:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? We need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us why!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Chieko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are ALL of you quitting?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have so much to learn! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't even say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay with us forever, Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you, be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had people quit before, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they have their reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.08,0:21:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Marilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing. Forcing you to stay\Nwould only make us all uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, about your new foreman...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.75,0:21:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping I could ask you, Marilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Marilla? Our foreman?\NThen we've nothing to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no! Wait a minute! Just hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I can't be foreman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who else could I ask to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If Marilla won't do it, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll give everyone three lunch breaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I volunteer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.92,0:21:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll double our wages!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll turn the mill into a flower garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, Marilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Foreman Marilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't be as forgiving as Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.42,0:21:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you tell Chieko something for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.58,0:21:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know what's going on in her life...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:21:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell her, "Don't let it beat you."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.25,0:22:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You think the girls at the laundry mill\Nwill get on without us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.33,0:22:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.79,0:22:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They are now strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.08,0:22:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain they'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.33,0:22:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
